This document list the possible use cases for the Crime analysis.
1. Create data summary
2. A graph that illustrates the crime count in every borough with respect to year: Work in Progress (Joby)
3. The type of crime that was most frequently committed.
4. Subtype of the crime that was most frequently committed.
5. Trend analysis of crimes committed over time.
6. Time of occurrence and location of a crimes.
7. Exploratory analysis of the crime against different dataset like premise of crime occurrence to link the crime data to the premise data.
